    <h2>My Story</h2>
    <p>For 10+ years, I worked as a pediatric speech-language pathologist, helping young children overcome communication challenges and supporting their families through the journey. I saw firsthand how important nutrition and wellness were for my patients' development and my own family's health.</p>
    <p>When I became a stay-at-home mom, I discovered that finding quality wellness products — clean supplements, organic foods, natural skincare — was time-consuming and expensive. I was spending hours hunting for deals just to make healthy choices affordable for our family of 7.</p>
    <p>That's why I started <strong>Wellness Savings</strong>. I wanted to create the resource I wish I'd had: a place where busy parents and wellness-conscious families can find <strong>verified discount codes</strong> and <strong>honest product reviews</strong> — all in one place.</p>

    <h2>What Wellness Savings Offers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Curated deals:</strong> I personally vet every discount code before sharing it with you.</li>
      <li><strong>Honest reviews:</strong> Products I recommend are ones I've researched, tested, or genuinely trust.</li>
      <li><strong>Real savings:</strong> From supplements and organic coffee to skincare and baby essentials — every deal is verified and updated.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Trust Me?</h2>
    <p>With a decade of clinical experience in pediatric healthcare and years of navigating wellness as a mom of 5, I bring both professional knowledge and real-life perspective to every recommendation. I know what it's like to want the best for your family while sticking to a budget — and I'm here to help you do exactly that.</p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>Have a question, a deal tip, or a product you'd like me to review? I'd love to hear from you! Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@wellnesssavings.org">hello@wellnesssavings.org</a> or <a href="/contact/">visit my contact page</a>.</p>

    <h2>How Wellness Savings Makes Money</h2>
    <p>This site is supported by affiliate commissions and display ads. When you purchase through my links, I may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. I only recommend products I genuinely believe in — my integrity and your trust matter more than any commission.</p>
